Package: hrmn
Title: Harmonize Datasets
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R:
    person("Jon", "Harmon", , "jonthegeek@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4781-4346"))
Description: A common early step during data analysis is "data
    harmonization" -- converting disparate datasets into a unified,
    consistent format, with consistent column names, classes, and values.
    The goal of 'hrmn' is to make this process as easy as it can be.
